                        <p>
                            <bold>Methods:</bold>
                        </p>
                    </list-item>
                    <list-item>
                        <p>The methods section could be broken into two sub-sections: (1) describing the interview sample, interview protocol, and data analysis methods; and (2) the framework for analyzing the ESCO business models.</p>
                    </list-item>
                    <list-item>
                        <p>The current methods section is too short and doesn&#x2019;t provide enough empirical grounding for the rest of the paper.</p>
                    </list-item>
                </list> &#x00a0; 
